snippet.title: Rocket Racing Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Race without limits. There's no right or wrong way to race as long as you're headed to the top! In this all-new competitive racing experience, you'll be one of 12 total racers on a track where dodging obstacles, timing your boosts, and using flips, flying, and drifts will be the difference between being left behind and claiming victory.

Rocket Racing launches with a number of tracks with different challenges in each environment. In addition, this experience hits the starting line with a lineup of cars available for purchase in the Shop. Some of those include Rocket League classics like: Jager, and Cyclone and an introduction to Diesel.

In Rocket Racing Season Zero, put your skills to the test in 26 tracks. Avoid towering obstacles, take shortcuts, and flip onto walls to blast past your competition. This is just the start of the race with new modes, tracks, and more in 2024!

Take your favorite Rocket League cars on new adventures! All players have a Locker in Fortnite, and in the “Cars” section you can equip a car to use in Rocket Racing. 

Rocket Racing is now available to play in Fortnite. 

#RocketRacing #RaceWithoutLimits
